SUMMARY: 

This notice publishes the ``Report to OPM on Living Costs in Hawaii, Guam and the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana
Islands, Puerto Rico, United States Virgin Islands, and in the Washington, DC, Area, March 1994,'' prepared by Runzheimer
International under Government contract OPM-90-0705. This report provides the basis for the increases
in certain cost-of-living allowances (COLA's) being proposed by OPM in the notice of proposed rulemaking immediately
preceding this notice.



