Runzheimer included the average annual cost of financing a vehicle in the total cost of private transportation. Runzheimer
surveyed automobile dealerships in Puerto Rico and banks in all other areas for their auto-loan interest rates, using
a 48-month loan length with 80% financing as the basis in all locations.



