(d) 

Key personnel

. (10 points). 

(1) The Secretary reviews each application to determine the quality of key personnel the applicant plans to use on
the project, including_

(i) The qualifications of the project director; 

(ii) The qualifications of each of the other key personnel to be used on the project; 

(iii) The time, including justification for the time that each one of the key personnel, including the project director,
will commit to the project; and 

(iv) Subject to the Indian preference provisions of the Indian Self-Determination Act (25 U.S.C. 450 

